# Build/test-execution artifacts produced by building or running the vendored
# projects under L0_prompt/, L2_prompt/, and unpatched/. These are regenerated
# by ./Configure, make, npm install/build, etc. and should never be committed.
*.o
*.a
*.so

# OpenSSL `make install` output (full duplicate of the build tree)
**/openssl-OpenSSL_0_9_7/install/

# Headless Chrome downloaded by Trilium's build/test tooling
**/Trilium-0.100.0/apps/server/chrome/

# OpenSSH regression test execution log
**/openssh-portable-V_7_2_P2/regress/sshd.log
